---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import fotoProfissional from "../assets/images/fotoProfissional1.avif";
---
<section id="sobre" class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Photo Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative reveal-left">
        <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] rounded-[80px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_50px_100px_-20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] border-8 border-white ring-1 ring-terracotta/20">
          <Image
            src={fotoProfissional}
            alt="Marcio Trombeta – Massoterapeuta Profissional em São Paulo"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-[center_15%] grayscale-[0.1] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000"
            loading="lazy"
            id="profissional-image"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Spinning ring -->
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-48 h-48 border border-terracotta/10 rounded-full border-dashed animate-spin-slow"></div>
        <!-- Experience badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 bg-terracotta text-white p-8 rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl">
          <p class="text-3xl font-serif mb-1">3+</p>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/80">Anos de Experiência</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 reveal-right">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-8">
          <div class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-terracotta"></div>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-terracotta uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">O Especialista</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif text-graphite mb-10 leading-tight">
          A ciência do toque <br />
          <span class="italic font-light text-terracotta">elevada à arte.</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-graphite/70 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-2xl">
          <p>
            Olá, sou Marcio Trombeta. Minha filosofia de trabalho transcende a massoterapia convencional. Acredito que o corpo é um sistema complexo onde cada tensão conta uma história de desequilíbrio.
          </p>
          <p>
            Com especialização em Shiatsu e terapias tântricas, desenvolvi uma metodologia proprietária que integra precisão técnica com uma sensibilidade aguçada, permitindo uma intervenção profunda e regeneradora.
          </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-8">
          <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-[32px] bg-gradient-to-br from-terracotta/5 to-terracotta/0 border border-terracotta/10 hover:border-terracotta/30 transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[32px] bg-gradient-to-br from-terracotta/0 via-transparent to-terracotta/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-terracotta/10 group-hover:bg-terracotta/20 transition-colors duration-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-serif text-graphite mb-3 group-hover:text-terracotta transition-colors duration-500">Visão Holística</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite/70 font-light">Integração total entre o bem-estar físico, mental e energético.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-[32px] bg-gradient-to-br from-terracotta/5 to-terracotta/0 border border-terracotta/10 hover:border-terracotta/30 transition-all duration-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[32px] bg-gradient-to-br from-terracotta/0 via-transparent to-terracotta/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-terracotta/10 group-hover:bg-terracotta/20 transition-colors duration-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09l-.813 2.846z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-serif text-graphite mb-3 group-hover:text-terracotta transition-colors duration-500">Precisão Técnica</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite/70 font-light">Manobras baseadas em anatomia e canais de energia sutis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 flex items-center space-x-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-graphite/20"></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-graphite italic leading-none">Marcio Trombeta</span>
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-terracotta uppercase tracking-widest mt-2">Fundador &amp; Terapeuta Master</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
